# --- Python ---
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# --- Audio policy ---
# ALL audio is committed (source test signals AND competitor masters) so the full
# dataset travels with the repo: a fresh clone has everything needed to continue.
# The bootstrap spec gitignored competitor masters for leanness; we override that
# to keep the corpus portable across machines. If the audio corpus grows large
# (full 64-master matrix + more services), migrate WAVs to Git LFS.
#
# source/original-references/ was removed by the operator; no rule needed.

# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.tmp
